Kaburkan penilaian anda, Qu Bai.

00:13:49.240 --> 00:13:50.040
Adakah begitu?

00:13:51.440 --> 00:13:52.520
Kenapa saya rasa

00:13:53.560 --> 00:13:55.620
bahawa anda mengambil berat tentang dia lebih daripada saya?

00:13:55.760 --> 00:13:56.160
awak...

