00:15:43.200 --> 00:15:45.720
Old K benar-benar telah menimbulkan orang gila.

00:15:46.400 --> 00:15:48.760
Adakah anda fikir bukti anda tidak bernilai

00:15:49.440 --> 00:15:50.440
