00:15:58.920 --> 00:16:00.520
Pihak hospital hanya menghantar berita.

00:16:00.560 --> 00:16:02.000
Yu Jia belum mati.

00:16:02.240 --> 00:16:04.360
Dia kini di bawah perlindungan polis.

00:16:05.040 --> 00:16:06.480
Sebaik sahaja Yu Jia bangun,

